Specifically about pledge/mortage
.:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
The following additional provisions apply for loans and credits secured by
pledge/mortgage.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
...UDENOM
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
1. Extent of the security
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Pledge/mortgage serves as security for payment of funds, interest,
commission, legal costs and other expenses incurred in connection with
recovery of debt.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
Pledge/mortgage applied by you serves as security for any obligation you
have or may have in the future towards &BANKNAVN..
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. has a free choice of which part of the consolidated credit
balance, or which credit balance out of two or more, must be reduced by
means of the pledge/mortgage.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2. Insurance of pledged/mortgaged effects
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If &BANKNAVN. has pledge/mortgage on car, boat, other movables or real
property, the pledger is obliged to take out a comprehensive motor
and/or fire insurance covering the pledged/mortgaged effects.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the pledge/mortgage is applied by third party, you are obliged to pay
the insurance premium, if not paid by third party.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3. Depreciation of pledge/mortgage
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the value of the pledge/mortgage is considerably
depreciated, &BANKNAVN. may require that you either extraordinarily reduce
your debt/credit limit or that additional funding is made available
corresponding to the actual depreciation. Otherwise, &BANKNAVN. may
consider the loan/credit as non-performing.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, if &BANKNAVN. has mortgage on real property which serves as
your permanent residence, &BANKNAVN. will not require extraordinary
settlement in case the property value is depreciated, or other
security unless the depreciation is due to mismanagement.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4. &BANKNAVN.'s right to pledged/mortgaged effects
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. may use all rights of the pledger to the pledged/mortgaged
effects, including receiving and confirming the receipt of any
amount according to the pledged/mortgaged effects, terminating
and collecting, signing and transferring pledged claims and
mortgaging deeds to the bank or others, and withdrawing amounts
from pledged deposit accounts.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the event that shares etc. are pledged, &BANKNAVN. may exercise all
rights of shareholders according to current company laws, articles of
association, owner agreements, if any, etc. However, the voting right lies
with the pledger, until &BANKNAVN. clearly notifies that the bank wants
to make use of this right. If &BANKNAVN. requires so, the pledger must
forward notification from the company, including, but not limited
to, notices and minutes of annual general meetings.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the pledge comprises insurance policies, the pledger is obliged, on
demand, to present &BANKNAVN. to proper receipt for timely
payment of the premium.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
If &BANKNAVN. chooses to seek satisfaction in the buyback value of the
policy, &BANKNAVN. must be entitled to do so without having to await the
the notice laid down in the national insurance contract law.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. are not obliged to seek cover in the applied pledge/mortgage in
advance, just as &BANKNAVN. has freedom of choice regarding use in
relation to the consolidated commitment.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
5. Pledge/mortgage-related expenses
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. may require payment of expenses for pledged/mortgaged effects.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may also require payment of &BANKNAVN.'s expenses in connection
with the handling of its interests as pledgee, including any expenses in
connection with payment of insurance premium, inspection of the
pledged/mortgaged effects, costs in connection with legal advice, etc.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
6. Return of investment on the pledge/mortgage
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 2mm
The pledging/mortgaging comprises any interest and dividend of the
pledged/mortgaged effect(s), including bonus of life insurance policies,
any bonus shares and rights of shares, revenue of drawn bonds, rental, etc.
.sp 2mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. is entitled, but not bound (neither in relation to third party
guarantors) to receive interest or dividend for payment of
instalments, interest and expenses.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
