9. Expiry
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Pledge/mortgage applied by third party expires after 10
years, however, after 5 years in case of pledge/mortgage with floating
loan amount and loans without fixed due date. &BANKNAVN.'s claim
against the third party pledger does not expire, if the claim
is sustained by &BANKNAVN. prior to this.
