10. Reversal
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the pledged secured loan/credit is repaid, fully or partly, and the
payments are set aside at a later point in time, the pledger is bound to
establish the pledge/mortgage of &BANKNAVN., whether &BANKNAVN. has
released the pledge or not.
