12. Enforcement
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Any realisation of mortgage takes place after prior notice to the pledger
on transaction or otherwise, which &BANKNAVN. considers
expedient, including realisation on &BANKNAVN.'s own arrangement.
